.TP 8n
.B -Edit
.br
Edit the attributes with a text editor,
this is usually more convenient than supplying a text file.
The
.I EDITOR
environment variable will be consulted for the name of the editor to use;
defaults to
.IR vi (1)
if not set.
Warning:
not well behaved when faced with errors,
the temporary file is always deleted.
